response_parts.content:
{
  "response": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "translated": "[CORNER: Song Watchalong] I'd like to talk about the music after we watch the 3DMV"
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "translated": "that was specially written for this event."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "translated": "Please take a look."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "Breathing inside a borrowed life and a body that can't become anything,"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "if I dive deep into the depths, the me from that day"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "is still smiling."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "If I look back, they certainly remain—"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "the fragments of dreams that sprouted in my heart."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "Crushed by the shadow of ideals, it eventually turned into hatred. Even if I regret the past, it can't be helped, right?"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "A tiny, gentle light..."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "The feelings I believed in still don't reach."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "Even so, I want to draw more of the future with these hands on the pure white scenery that remains dry before my eyes."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "Even if it's not beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "I want to keep drawing"
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "this world as it appears to me,"
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": "in my own way."
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": "And there we go. Sorry,"
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "my screen just... excuse me."
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "That was the 3DMV for the song written by Chochop-san for this event. This is the first time the title has been revealed!"
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "The name of the song is \"Sono E no Namae wa\" (The Name of That Painting)."
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "translated": "Wait,"
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "translated": "first... oh,"
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "translated": "never mind."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "translated": "I thought my notes were Chochop-san's comments, and I was like, \"Wait, the outfit?\""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "translated": "But I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "translated": "This is actually"
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "translated": " the memo I sent to the staff beforehand."
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "translated": "Let me read it."
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "translated": "\"Just listening to it makes me feel Ena's journey, and it brings me to tears."
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "translated": "The title contains the kanji for 'E' and 'Na' from her name, so I felt it was truly a song that depicts Ena."
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "translated": "Instead of just letting the regret, frustration, and pain be, I sang with the resolve to turn them into strength,"
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "translated": "and with the positive feelings she found once she made that decision.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "translated": "That's what the past version of me emailed to the staff."
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "translated": "As for Chochop-san's comments, they've been shared on the ProSeka Broadcasting Station"
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "translated": "and on Twitter—"
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "translated": "well, X—so please check them out there."
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "translated": "But yeah, those were the feelings I put into the song."
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "translated": "There are lyrics that feel like she's looking back at the past, but"
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "translated": "it feels like the current Ena is the one doing the reflecting."
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "translated": "I think Ena definitely has regrets, but she's the kind of girl who understands that she is who she is now because of them."
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "translated": "So, even for the phrases about the past, I didn't want to sing them with total agony like the old Ena would have."
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "translated": "I was very conscious of that while recording."
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "translated": "I sang with that sense of resolve,"
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "translated": "and like I mentioned during the story discussion,"
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "translated": "with that sense of relief and the newfound brightness she finally found."
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "translated": "But this isn't the goal yet;"
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "translated": "it's a new start."
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "translated": "I tried to capture that middle ground of emotions"
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "translated": "while I was singing."
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "translated": "So, rather than one big explosion of emotion,"
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "translated": "it's more like quietly simmering the words inside and encouraging herself."
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "translated": "Like she's patting her own chest to say, \"I can do this.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "translated": "I sang it with that kind of self-encouragement in mind."
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "translated": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "translated": "Man, it really does make me cry."
    }
  ]
}

